hated secret police often used to suppress any signs of dissent 
prodemocracy activists had demanded the breakup of both the 
militia and the secret police as the country moves toward free 
elections in may 
the militia once armed with antiaircraft guns automatic 
weapons armored personnel carriers and rocketpropelled grenades 
