federal reserve system are dominated by members chosen by bankers 
gonzalez through most of his 28year career in congress has 
been frequently critical of the central bank for fighting inflation 
at the expense of economic growth when interest rates soared in 
the early 1980s he introduced legislation to impeach paul volcker 
then fed chairman 
