in tiny rings of pale grey rubber and sells for a measly 35 
the years best seller may be the montblanc the product of an 
81yearold west german company topped with a signature white 
snowcap reminiscent of its namesake europes highest peak 
montblanc pens sell for 100 to 7000 each 
